      <h2 style="margin-top: var(--space-7);">Coverage by Region</h2>
      <ul style="color: var(--ink-muted); padding-left: var(--space-5);">
        <li><strong>Western Europe:</strong> Full live overlap. CET, GMT, BST — all covered in standard working hours.</li>
